Bhasma(Vibhuti) Dharane:
Manastoketi kutso rudro jagati; bhasma dhAraNe viniyogah. 
Om. manasto ke tanaye ma na ayushi mano goshu mano ashveshu ririshah |
viranmano rudra bhamito vadhir havishmamto namasa vidhemate ||
TryAyusham jamadagnih iti lalate.
Kashyapasya TryAyusham iti kanthe.
Agastyasya TryAyusham iti nabhau.
Yad devanam TryAyusham iti dakshina bhuje. 
Tan me astu TryAyusham iti vama bhuje.
Sarvam astu shatayusham iti shirasi.
balayushamiti sarvange

Pranayama:
pranavasya parabrahma rishih |daivi gayatri chchhamdah |parabrahma paramatma devata |
pranayame viniyogah ||
Om bhuh, Om bhuvah, Om suvah, Om mahah, Om janah, Om tapah, Om satyam
<<<<<<<<<GAYATRI MANTRA>>>>>>>>>
omapo jyoti rasomritam brahma bhurbhuvassuvarom ||
mamopatta samasta duritakshayadvara, shri parameshvaraprityartham, pratah (sayam) samdhyam upasishye |

Marjana:
Apohishtethi tisranam ambarisha sindhu dveepa RishiH; Apo devata; Gayatri chandaH marjane viniyogaH

Om apohishtha mayo bhuvah | (chest)
ta na urje dadhatana| (throat)
mahe ranaya chakshase| (belly)
yo vah shivatamo rasah| (right)
tasya bhajayateha nah| (left)
ushatiriva matarah| (legs)
tasma aramga mamavah| (back)
yasya kshayaya jinvatha| (neck)
apo janayatha cha nah||(face)

Mantrachamane:
(Morning)
Om suryashcha ma manyushcha manyu patayashcha manyu kritebhyah | 
papebhyo rakshamtam | 
yadratriya papa makarsham | 
manasa vacha hastabhyam | 
padbhya mudarena shishnja | 
ratristadavalumpatu | 
yatkimcha duritam mayi | 
idamaham mamamritayonau | 
surye jyotishi juhomi svaha ||

(Evening)
Om agnishcha ma manyushcha manyu patayashcha manyu kritebhyah | 
papebhyo rakshamtam | 
yadahna papa makarsham | 
manasa vacha hastabhyam | 
padbhya mudarena shishnja | 
ahastadavalumpatu | 
yatkimcha duritam mayi | 
idamaham mamamritayonau | 
satye jyotishi juhomi svaha ||

Repeat Aachamana:
Repeat Marjana:

