dik namaskaara
morning stand facing east (turn and stop at 8 directions)
indraaya namaha
agnaye namaha
yamaya namaha
nirutaye namaha
varunaaya namaha
vayave namaha
kuberaya namaha
ishaanaya namaha

Evening stand facing west (turn and stop at 8 directions)
varunaaya namaha
vayave namaha
kuberaya namaha
ishaanaya namaha
indraaya namaha
agnaye namaha
yamaya namaha
nirutaye namaha


(morning) anena pratah sandhya vandana gayatri japa karmana bhagavan sarvatmaka sri parameshvara priyatam
(evening) anena sayama sandhya vandana gayatri japa karmana bhagavan sarvatmaka sri parameshvara priyatam

japa kaale madhye sarva lopa prayachitartham namatrya japam karishye
om achyutaya namaha, anantaya namaha, govindaya namaha (3 times)

